### Créer un utilisateur admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@taskflow.dev",
  "name": "Alice Dupont",
  "password": "MotDePasse123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Créer un utilisateur viewer
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json  

{
  "email": "charlie@taskflow.dev",
  "name": "Charlie Viewer",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "viewer"
}

### Lister les utilisateurs (sans passwordHash)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMDQ4MWI1Yy02MmZiLTQzZmEtOTk1NC1jODdmM2UxNThhZGEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFsaWNlQHRhc2tmbG93LmRldiIsInJvbGUiOiJtZW1iZXIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzczMDE0ODQsImV4cCI6MTc3NzMwNTA4NH0.ZIYP5vh5-M1ACKs-ExCUyRqu8EONgtCJWxgkyTNKSho

### Récupérer par ID (remplacer l'UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/REMPLACER_PAR_UUID

### UUID malformé → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/pas-un-uuid

### Modifier le profil de Bob (remplacer l'UUID et le token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/20481b5c-62fb-43fa-9954-c87f3e158ada
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMDQ4MWI1Yy02MmZiLTQzZmEtOTk1NC1jODdmM2UxNThhZGEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFsaWNlQHRhc2tmbG93LmRldiIsInJvbGUiOiJtZW1iZXIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzczMDE0ODQsImV4cCI6MTc3NzMwNTA4NH0.ZIYP5vh5-M1ACKs-ExCUyRqu8EONgtCJWxgkyTNKSho
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "admin" }

### Supprimer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/20481b5c-62fb-43fa-9954-c87f3e158ada
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}